<topic id="ant-quick-assist">
  <title>Ant Quick Assist Support</title>
  <body>
    <p><uicontrol>Quick Assist</uicontrol> is activated automatically when the cursor is positioned
      over the name of a component. It is accessible via a yellow bulb help marker placed on the
      cursor line, in the editor line number stripe. Also, you can invoke the quick assist menu if
      you press <uicontrol conref="oxygen-shortcuts-list.dita#oxygen-shortcuts-list/alt_1"/> on your
      keyboard.</p>
